\size small 
Ejemplo Sea 
\begin_inset Formula $\dim\left[M\right]=3$
\end_inset 

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega=\omega_{1}dx^{1}+\omega_{2}dx^{2}+\omega_{3}dx^{3}$
